The DAO of Visionary Creators. Ecstatic Manifestation. All Genesis NFTs hold potent creative codes which also serve as your immutable membership to the Cosmic Assembly DAO. The opportunity to co-create a world of exclusive experiences, opportunities, and surprises. 

The sounds of the Cosmic Assembly Genesis Collection are tuned to the 528 Hz Solfeggio Frequency, which is also referred to as the love frequency. Resonating through the core of everything. Connecting our hearts, our multidimensional nature, and the divine harmony between masculine and feminine energies in all of us.

/Sounds produced by Walkerji

/Visual Artist Fernando D'Antonio

/Powered by Highvibe Network
